 (`input logic x, input logic y, output logic z`).\n*   When using `assign`, ensure the right-hand side expressions are valid logic expressions.\n*   Since this is combinational, an `always @(*)` block is not strictly necessary, but using a simple `assign` statement is superior for this simple logic.",
